  "title": "Optometrist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Looking for Part/Full time Retail Optometrists!</strong></p><p><strong>Fully Registered or Provisional all are welcome!</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Location: </strong>Tampines Central, Toa Payoh or Upper Serangoon</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><strong>1. Conduct Comprehensive Eye Examinations: </strong>Perform eye examinations to assess visual acuity, refractive errors, and overall eye health.</p><p><strong>2. Prescribe Contact Lenses: </strong>Determine the appropriate prescription for eyeglasses or contact lenses based on the results of eye examinations.<br />Provide guidance to patients on proper lens care and usage.</p><p><strong>3. Patient management: </strong>Help the patient choose the appropriate frames and lenses for their prescription and needs. Assist the patient when there are any difficulties and troubleshoot patient complaints<br /></p><p><strong>4. Monitor and Manage Myopia Control: </strong>Monitor and manage patient's eye health, tracking changes in vision and adjusting prescriptions as needed.<br />Educate patients on preventive eye care measures and lifestyle factors, as well as solutions that can help to slow down the progression of myopia. <br /></p><p><strong>5. Provide Patient Education: </strong>Communicate examination results and treatment plans to patients in a clear and concise manner.<br />Educate patients on maintaining good eye health and preventing eye-related issues.<br /></p><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Optometry </li><li>Must be registered with <strong>OOB</strong> in Singapore</li></ul>",
